<div class="modal-body">
	<label>This recording will be about publication</label>
	<p><%=@webinar.publication.title%></p>

	<span><label>Title </label> (you could edit the title later)</span>
	<p id="recording_title" type="text"><%=@webinar.title%>-<%=Time.now.to_formatted_s(:short)%></p>

	<label>To start the recording fill the title and then, in the popover in the left side:</label>
	<ol>
		<li>Select "IDeM" in the "Window to share" option</li>
		<li>Select the desired mic in the "Mic to share" option</li>
		<li>Click on "Share selected elements"</li>
	</ol>
</div>
<div class="modal-footer">
	<button type="button" class="button-secondary-orange" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
</div>